msgstr "namizje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; offers you the possibility to have several virtual desktops."
msgstr "&kde; vam nudi možnost številnih virtualnih namizij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the names to the desktops by clicking on the "
"<guibutton>Rename</guibutton> button (appears when you hover the desktop "
"item in the list) and entering text into the text field."
msgstr ""
"Imena namizij lahko spremenite tako, da kliknete gumb <guibutton>Preimenuj</"
"guibutton> (prikaže se, ko premaknete miškin kazalec na element namizja na "
"seznamu) in vnesete besedilo v besedilno polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to remove a desktop, use the trash overlay icon at the right of "
"the desktop item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti namizje, uporabite ikono koša na desni strani elementa "
"namizja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button to add a virtual desktop "
"(default name is <guilabel>New Desktop</guilabel>) to the list."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>, da dodate virtualno namizje "
"(privzeto ime je <guilabel>Novo namizje</guilabel>) na seznam."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the number of rows in the pager item on the panel. Just "
"use the rows input box below the list to adjust the number of desktops. The "
"desktops will be rearranged by the rows automatically."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirate lahko število vrstic v elementu pozivnika na plošči. Samo "
"uporabite polje za vnos vrstic pod seznamom, da prilagodite število namizij. "
"Namizja bodo samodejno prerazporejena po vrsticah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation wraps around"
msgstr "Obdaja ga navigacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this option if you want a keyboard or active desktop border "
"navigation beyond the edge of a desktop to take you to the opposite edge of "
"the new desktop."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite to možnost, če želite, da vas tipkovnica ali aktivna navigacija po "
"robu namizja popelje na nasprotni rob novega namizja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show animation when switching"
msgstr "Prikaži animacijo ob menjavi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Slide</guilabel>, <guilabel>Desktop Cube Animation</"
"guilabel>, or <guilabel>Fade Desktop</guilabel> from the drop-down box or "
"switch animations off by unchecking the item. If the selected animation has "
"settings options, click on the tools icon on the right of the drop-down box "
"to launch a configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem polju izberite <guilabel>Drsenje</guilabel>, <guilabel>Animacija "
"kocke</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Bledenje</guilabel> ali pa izklopite "
"animacije tako, da počistite polje. Če ima izbrana animacija možnosti "
"nastavitev, kliknite ikono orodij na desni strani spustnega menija, da "
"zaženete konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show on-screen display when switching"
msgstr "Pri preklopu pokaži prikaz na zaslonu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this option if you want to have an on-screen display for desktop "
"switching."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite to možnost, če želite imeti prikaz za preklapljanje med namizji na "
"zaslonu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show desktop layout indicators"
msgstr "Pokaži indikatorje postavitve namizja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enabling this option will show a small preview of the desktop layout "
"indicating the selected desktop."
msgstr ""
"Če omogočite to možnost, se prikaže majhen predogled postavitve namizja, ki "
"označuje izbrano namizje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scrolling the mouse wheel over an empty space on the desktop or on the "
"<guilabel>Pager</guilabel> icon in the panel will change to the next virtual "
"desktop numerically, in the direction you scrolled (either up or down)."
msgstr ""
"Če miškino kolesce pomaknete čez prazen prostor na namizju ali na ikono "
"<guilabel>Pozivnik</guilabel> na plošči, se bo namizje spremenilo v smeri, v "
"katero ste se pomaknili kolesce (navzgor ali navzdol), glede na "
"oštevilčenost namizij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change this default behavior on the page <guilabel>Mouse Actions</"
"guilabel> in the <guilabel>Desktop Settings</guilabel> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>, <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"To privzeto obnašanje lahko spremenite na strani <guilabel>Dejanja miške</"
"guilabel> v <guilabel>Nastavitve namizja</guilabel> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>, <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>)."

